N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2603.1 - Notice of funding availability

State Regulations

As funds are made available for the purposes of this
program, the division shall publish in the State Register notice of the
availability of funds and procedures for obtaining and submitting
applications. Notes
